<L>Impa&s;&s;ion'd, fickle, giv'n to pride,</L>
<L><PB N="220" REF="237">Nor re&s;ting e'er &s;elf-&s;atisfied,</L>
<L>Doth pow'r comparative t'improve <MILESTONE N="175"></L>
<L>Perfection po&s;itive remove?</L>
