<L>At flames, that all to ruin turn,</L>
<L>Annihilating as they burn?</L>
<L>Ri&s;k'd, then, the cen&s;ure of my wit,</L>
<L>I hold the world unfini&s;h'd yet:</L>
<L><PB N="223" REF="240">Time building what Heav'n's wi&s;dom plann'd,</L>
