<L>Leaves no identity behind.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L>But waving this, yet &s;ee we here</L>
<L>No ab&s;tract cau&s;e of ill, to fear:<MILESTONE N="240"></L>
<L>Since on the feelings of mankind</L>
<L><PB N="224" REF="241">Depends the ev'ry ill we find:</L>
<L>Whence, tho' our &s;uff'rings ill we call,</L>
