<L>Yet, ev'n while tears of angui&s;h flow,<MILESTONE N="265"></L>
<L>I hold no ab&s;tract ill we know.</L>
<L>'Tis true, my friend, no man alive</L>
<L>Could, in his &s;en&s;es, gravely &s;trive</L>
<L>The wretch in torture to per&s;uade</L>
