<L>'Tis not by exta&s;y alone <MILESTONE N="325"></L>
<L>Thy actual &s;hare of joy is known:</L>
<L><PB N="229" REF="246"><HI>Duration</HI> adds to the degree</L>
<L>As much as its <HI>inten&s;ity.</HI></L>
