<L>Heav'n's good depends upon our own.<MILESTONE N="410"></L>
</LG>
<LG>
<L><HI>Lorenzo,</HI> merely to mankind</L>
<L>Thus evil <HI>phy&s;ical</HI> confin'd;</L>
